{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/1-06182023111246.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-06-18T11:15:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-06-18T13:41:53-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u7f8e\u4e2d\u7ade\u4e89\u5347\u7ea7   \u300a\u79d1\u6280\u5408\u4f5c\u534f\u8bae\u300b\u524d\u666f\u582a\u5fe7", "description": "\u8def\u900f\u793e6\u670818\u65e5\u5f15\u8ff0\u591a\u4f4d\u719f\u6089\u76f8\u5173\u8ba8\u8bba\u7684\u7f8e\u56fd\u5b98\u65b9\u6d88\u606f\u4eba\u58eb\u62ab\u9732\uff0c\u6709\u9274\u4e8e\u76ee\u524d\u7f8e\u4e2d\u5173\u7cfb\u5904\u4e8e\u6570\u5341\u5e74\u6765\u6700\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u72b6\u6001\uff0c\u7f8e\u56fd\u653f\u5e9c\u5185\u90e8\u6b63\u5c31\u662f\u5426\u8ba9\u300a\u7f8e\u4e2d\u79d1\u6280\u5408\u4f5c\u534f\u5b9a\u300b(STA)\u5728\u4eca\u5e74\u665a\u4e9b\u65f6\u5019\u5931\u6548\u8fdb\u884c\u8ba8\u8bba\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": [], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/1-06182023111246.html/@@images/2eb50be4-be70-48f0-82ca-e2cc1f62068c.jpeg\"/>\n\u7f8e\u4e2d\u4e24\u56fd\u56fd\u65d7\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/1-06182023111246.html/@@images/image\">\n <img src=\"https://www.rfa.org//++plone++rfa-resources/img/icon-zoom.png\"/>\n</a>\n\u7f8e\u8054\u793e\u56fe\u7247\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u7f8e\\u4e2d\\u7ade\\u4e89\\u5347\\u7ea7   \\u300a\\u79d1\\u6280\\u5408\\u4f5c\\u534f\\u8bae\\u300b\\u524d\\u666f\\u582a\\u5fe7\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n                    \"media_name\": \"aud